Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:37.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Two months have passed since the Macross,\Njust prior to its launch ceremony,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:41.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,executed a sudden space fold and was instantly\Ntransported inside the orbit of Pluto.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:46.59,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is currently\Nheaded back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:51.88,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,It fended off a Zentradi attack by\Nmaking a transformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,but the change in the ship's structure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:58.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,caused a great deal of casualties\Namong the refugees on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:02.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the people have\Nsince rebuilt their city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.32,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(82,134)}DAEDALUS ATTACK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.00,0:02:06.18,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and for the moment, things are\Npeaceful once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, having volunteered\Nfor military service,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:30.33,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru Ichijo has been undergoing the\Nrigorous training of a new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at last, came the day\Nof his first leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, let me carry that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:37.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:39.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes no difference to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:41.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.27,0:02:46.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.01,0:02:51.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you come look at them with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:52.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NYou want me to go in THAT store?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:56.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No choice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:02.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No peeking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:12.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's your lingerie corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is cute!\NWhat do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come back some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:37.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!\NI think it really suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it?\NThat abnormal energy reaction you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Captain.\NIt's a phenomenon we haven't seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the Fold System\Nused to be, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could there be some connection\Nbetween the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:08.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir. It's possible that the disappearance\Nof the Fold System resulted in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,a distortion of the space-time continuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:14.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?\NIs it interfering with any of the ship's systems?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at the moment, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NContinue with your analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:19.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:26.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can harness this energy, I believe\Nwe could create some kind of barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:29.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NGet started on it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:33.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?\NDo you have an explanation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've analyzed it\Nfrom every angle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:56.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just can't see the necessity\Nof adopting this configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:02.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,taking this shape would compromise\Ntheir gravity control system,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,greatly limiting their speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue playback, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.71,0:05:09.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's enough.\NReturn to the original image.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:09.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What planet is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fifth planet in\Nthis star system, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they'll try to lose\Nus in its vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:27.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they activate their ECM\Nwithin those rings,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be impossible for us\Nto pinpoint their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That plan is almost too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your opinion, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them attempt to carry out their plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:41.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When they run to the planet, we'll\Nhave them like vermin in a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:43.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:44.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!\NHikaru's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been about a month, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my imagination,\Nbut you look so grown up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Training you pretty hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:03.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, sit down. And you guys, too.\NHikaru isn't on display, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like business is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, eat up while they're still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:12.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!\NThere you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're about to get the order to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm gonna sortie already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!\NThe orders just came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Five recruits were formally assigned\Nto combat duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:28.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!\NCongratulations, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sit there.\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you all later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you're a real soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll even be moving from your communal\Nroom in the barracks to a private one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, just because you\Nhave your own room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:52.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean you can do any stupid thing you want.\NYou got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:02.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know 1st Lt. Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well, kinda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!\NIt's that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:07.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!\NMr. Lingerie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:08.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were in this lingerie shop, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:17.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Major Focker, is THIS the "fine recruit"\Nyou've taken under your wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:17.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru Ichijo, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:22.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Misa Hayase.\NHikaru Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I heard that\Nname before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So, this is the civilian?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:32.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That would explain why he\Ndidn't know anything."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hey, what's with the old lady?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"'Old lady'?!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So, even Hikaru thinks she\Nlooks like an old lady?"{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that civilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're that old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ulp!\NExcuse me, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:51.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's your superior now,\Nso you'd better watch what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to working with\Nyou in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I don't know\Nwhat you're into,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:02.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't look good for a man\Nto be going into those kinds of shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:03.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:24.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, electronic counter-measures\Nare now active.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they'll be able\Nto track us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What next, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We launch a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:32.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A surprise attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A surprise attack, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we leave Saturn, they'll\Nbe after us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:43.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to launch a sudden attack,\Nand then disengage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But, captain...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fully aware that it's a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:48.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reduce speed and begin\Npreparations for the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we will be luring the enemy\Nforce into Saturn's rings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:06.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and then hit them with a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can say at this point,\Nbut beyond that:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to show me your\Nhearts as true pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:12.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone you want to see,\Nsay your goodbyes to them tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!\NWaiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:34.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the big emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:40.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going into battle tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first day as a soldier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:45.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a wonderful pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll do great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, everyone's already\Nsays that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:55.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:02.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:06.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you look so lady-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:10.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After I went and wore the\Ndress we bought together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.\NIt really looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:13.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:14.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:17.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we get a picture\Nto remember this by?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I never look good in photos...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:27.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all.\NCome stand over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:28.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:56.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd better be getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:04.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm out alone with a guy for too long,\Nmy aunt and uncle get worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:05.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Well, be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could talk longer, but\Ngood luck tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:19.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...I could be dead, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, we can now activate\Nthe barrier system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:32.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:36.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the energy field simply\Ncan't completely cover the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:41.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The Macross is too big.\NThe system has its limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, this isn't an ideal solution, but...\NPlease observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemy attacks, we can\Nraise the barrier like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.03,0:11:51.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, should an attack approach\None of our vulnerable points,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we can move the barrier\Nto intercept, like so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The positioning is controlled\Nby the barrier system team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're calling the device\Nthe Pinpoint Barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a measly barrier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd still be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:18.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be up early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:22.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how nervous you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but count sheep or something\Nand just go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,His first mission.\NI'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:34.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The hours just before a battle\Nare the worst of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:07.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention Valkyrie squadrons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The surprise attack will take place\Nin the Cassini Divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:15.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Squadrons will assemble into seven groups\Nand stand by in the ice rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:19.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat, the surprise attack will\Ntake place in the Cassini Divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the same way before my first mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:29.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, one night without sleep won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:38.14,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,All Valkyrie squadrons, report to the\NPrometheus and confirm personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie Skull Squadron, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:11.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie Skull Squadron No. 23,\NHikaru Ichijo, now launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:11.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:25.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange, Purple, and Rose Valkyrie teams:\Nadvance into the rings...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,...and proceed to point R-18\Nin the Cassini Divide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lure the enemy ships into range\Nof the main cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:44.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why's everyone flying so dangerously?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull 23!\NWhy are you playing around like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:54.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you paying attention\Nat the briefing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:59.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of fancy flying will give\Nyou away to the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:02.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an aerobatics show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the others were all flying\Nreally dangerously, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and follow\Nyour orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to talk to a superior?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look around you, Mister!\NYou're the only one who's goofing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger, roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be\Ntougher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:28.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Leader to all units.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll soon be heading into the\Nplanet's shadow zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:35.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for ice.\NAnd keep your eyes on your instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the shadow zone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Skull 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your speed's dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:02.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say.\NI can't see a thing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. What happened to all that\Nconfidence you had earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How come I have to get bossed\Naround by some old lady
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,who's sitting somewhere nice and safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do hope he'll stop insulting\Nhis superior officers
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,by the time the attack starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.\NIt doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:23.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase, how long until the Valkyrie\Nsquadrons reach their targets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,About five more minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:29.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Once the enemy ship\Nenters the rings, we'll fire the main gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:31.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound firing stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You called me, Commander Britai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.73,0:16:55.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zeril, I want you to approach the\Nsixth planet and capture the enemy vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:55.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Preferably undamaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:16:59.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:04.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:17.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:31.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As weak as they are,\Nthey dare to attack us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:34.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their grasp of battle tactics is laughable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't realized we're holding back\Nin order to capture their vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:44.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we show them how terrifying\Nwe can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy vessel is approaching,\Nwithin the main gun's starboard firing arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!\NRaise the ship and fire the main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing main cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:22.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fire the main gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:27.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pinpoint Barrier system seems\Nto be preventing it from operating somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming missiles!\NActivate the Pinpoint Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:39.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!\NI'll never make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't attack from the side!\NCome from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What IS that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a fool of me, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Agh, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:26.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, Valkyrie Teams Green and\NBrown have been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rose Team is under heavy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's all up to Skull Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, why isn't the Macross\Nfiring the main gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:55.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, would it be possible to\Nconcentrate all the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:02.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Pinpoint Barrier to\Nthe front of the Daedalus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we could, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do it!\NI have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NI leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:14.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kim, Shammy. Assemble all the Destroids\Nat the bow of the Daedalus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:19.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia! Send the Macross straight\Ntoward the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:19.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:38.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An airlock...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship is closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!\NBlast them to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Daedalus Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:20.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:21:59.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:20.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:21.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:23.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.06,0:22:25.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Daedalus Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.31,0:22:26.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I could really become a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We may need to call in reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:48.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,With the destruction of the mother ship, the battle pod\Npilots lost their will to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:51.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and were soon defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.62,0:22:54.41,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it goes without saying that\NFocker, Hikaru, and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:56.50,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,also played an important role\Nin the enemy's defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:22:58.91,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, try as he might,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:04.00,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru could not erase the image of the\Nterrified soldier's face from his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.12,0:23:08.42,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, when faced with\Na flesh-and-blood person,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:12.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru had found himself unable\Nto pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:16.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Focker-Sempai told him that\Nhe was no different at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:21.43,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Now able unflinchingly to pull\Nthe trigger against enemy ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:29.29,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru felt that somewhere in his heart,\Nhe was losing touch with his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:36.22,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(58,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:36.22,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(276,449)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:43.29,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Mars: home to an abandoned base\Nfrom the Unification Wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:48.13,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross sets course for Mars\Nin search of supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:53.48,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But for Misa, the planet brings\Nback heartbreaking memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.64,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.56,0:24:02.43,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(83,124)}BYE-BYE MARS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:23:59.07,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"BYE-BYE MARS"
