Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:29.92,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}the shadow you cast as you run away{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:36.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}We all keep running until the end,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:44.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}but we still can't see the goal{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:50.94,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}What awaits us after today?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.31,0:24:56.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}What awaits us beyond tomorrow?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:25:04.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}Even now, I keep running toward{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:15.85,songM,,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38)}the light that shines so far away{\b0}
